Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:17:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the frustration of that desire leading to anger and the energy of that anger being utilized
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to create whole social movements changes in the legislature and social changes such as we see
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,still going on the energy of that well anger as we experience it in daily life
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is usually in the form of resentments hatred grievances grudges of course eventually murder and
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,war the process going on in consciousness is one of expansion so the animal that is angry swells up
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you know when my cat gets angry her tail swells up she swells to almost twice her size and tries
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.52,0:17:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to look imposing so that's the biologic purpose expansion to overshadow one's apparently
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,an enemy so angriness the energy of that can be utilized to want something better for yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and move up to pride want something better for yourself use the energy of the frustration and
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:18:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the anger and move up to pride pride as you see is 175 which is enough to run the united states
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,marine corps it still however has a negative direction and we know that was it pride and
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.26,0:18:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,precedes the fall etc so there's many
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,things indicating that pride is not a very good thing it's good as compared to these lower fields
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,because it has much more energy and pride as we experience it in daily life is in the form of
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.51,0:18:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,arrogance contempt sarcasm the downside of it really is denial and the problem is and the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.19,0:18:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,process and consciousness is one of inflation so we say the person in pride then is arrogant has
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,a swelled head is too big for his britches is unteachable
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you know cannot hear that cannot hear and so those people have a closed mind so this position here
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,leads to a polarized position which puts the person therefore constantly on the defensive
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:19:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,of me being right and the world therefore must be wrong and so the energy is dissipated here
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in endless defensiveness of course the reason for for pride has to do with the underlying fear once
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the person faces the underlying fear they can let them let go of the pride
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,so one thing about these negative uh fields is that they tend to reinforce each other seldom do
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you see just one alone one predominates but they are really all feeding into each other
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,so that one has grief over one's anger one has anger over one's pride one has
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,fear over one's grief etc so that they all tend to reinforce each other so an upset is usually
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.73,0:19:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,composed of a composite of all these negative energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Something crucial happens now at the level of courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.82,0:19:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And courage, which calibrates at 200, has an enormous amount of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.82,0:19:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious that courage settled the United States of America.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:19:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Courage created all the great industries.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:20:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Courage is the basis of man's getting to the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.08,0:20:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So courage has an enormous amount of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.08,0:20:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, the Marines starts at pride but really hopes to move you up
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to a more stable level called courage. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not so much the increase or the increment of 25 points in the energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,although that is sizable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The critical thing is that the energy field now goes neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.08,0:20:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason for that is that the person has told the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the integrity scale,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and this is nothing but an adaptation of the integrity scale
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,combined with psychoanalysis and various other fields from geomancy, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you tell the truth, then, you're above the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no longer a victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And the reason is the energy field now
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.50,0:20:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,goes neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So you might say that this field here is like an antenna.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.50,0:20:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And below the level of courage, the antenna is tuned to the negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It pulls detriment into the energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:21:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So in geomancy, let's say, if we fly over an area,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,we can tell by just looking at a certain canyon
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that the energy field of that canyon is in a negative direction
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,by the way the flora lays out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field then is attuned to the negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.85,0:21:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now here, suddenly, it goes neutral,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,so that the energy field stops pulling to itself detriment from the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.85,0:21:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The person now is in a different condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.49,0:21:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They're now able to face things, face and cope and handle,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.49,0:21:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and the first time they're able to be appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.49,0:21:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So all these energy fields below here, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,courage still will experience these lesser feelings, these negative feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But the person in courage now has the power,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,to handle those negative energies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the process that's critical is one of empowerment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The person becomes re-empowered by telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, this is critical in the recovery from all illnesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.49,0:22:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and is very visibly so in Alcoholics Anonymous, let's say,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.49,0:22:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,where the first step is the admission of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.49,0:22:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens then to the person's energy fields,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.49,0:22:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,as you can test with kinesiology,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.49,0:22:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of going weak, the person suddenly goes strong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.49,0:22:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,when they admit that they are poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.49,0:22:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They're powerless over something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.49,0:22:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When we admit we don't know something,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.49,0:22:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,we get off the arrogance of pride and pretending that we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.16,0:22:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So the person may still have negative feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.16,0:22:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So the person in level of courage is going to ask the boss for a raise, for instance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.16,0:22:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,His stomach may still be in a knot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.16,0:22:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He might be angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.16,0:22:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He might even feel hopeless that he's going to get the raise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He might even be arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.16,0:22:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But now he has enough power to handle all that and be appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.16,0:22:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's able to face it and cope with it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.16,0:22:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and able to function in an effective way in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.16,0:22:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That brings us to the next level,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.96,0:22:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,where now you see the energy field swings to the right,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.96,0:22:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is positive, that which is aligned with the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.96,0:22:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And the energy field jumps to 250,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.96,0:23:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and this one is called neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And the emotion that goes with neutral is one of unattached, non-attachment,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.96,0:23:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,so that it's okay if you get the job and it's okay if you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.96,0:23:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The process going on in consciousness is we say the person is now released.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.99,0:23:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not attached to any particular outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.99,0:23:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They're no longer a victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.99,0:23:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The person now has a great deal more power.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.99,0:23:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we say no aversions, no attachments.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.99,0:23:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The person has no attachments and no aversions,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.99,0:23:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,meaning that they are now above the solar plexus.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.79,0:23:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Unattached, the downside of unattached can be detached or flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.79,0:23:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the upside of it can be the okayness of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.79,0:23:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,so that if you don't get this job, you'll get another job.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.79,0:23:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So the person is no longer a victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.79,0:23:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's no longer a leaf in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.79,0:23:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And the person's now feeling released
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.79,0:24:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore in a much better state, in a far more powerful state.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.18,0:24:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see the way that person sees the world is okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.18,0:24:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and the way they experience God is freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.18,0:24:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So the person then talks about,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.18,0:24:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, going free, God as being freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.18,0:24:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And they talk about, you know, detachment and feeling released.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.91,0:24:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The next energy field above that is called willingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.91,0:24:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Willingness, you see, at 310 is far more powerful to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.91,0:24:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And the emotion of that is accompanied by the thoughts of yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.91,0:24:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Saying yes to life, to join, to agree, to commit, to align with.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.91,0:24:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Because now we have the introduction of intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.91,0:24:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So a person on the level of neutral, let's say,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.14,0:24:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you say to them, would you like to go to a movie tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.14,0:24:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They say, well, it's okay if we go, and it's okay if we don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.14,0:24:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's not exactly enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.14,0:24:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not exactly aliveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.14,0:25:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's a long way from abundance yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.14,0:25:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And certainly far more comfortable than being down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.14,0:25:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,To be detached feels more comfortable than being in fear or grief or apathy or anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.14,0:25:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is still a far cry from willing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.68,0:25:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, waitress who perfunctorily,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.68,0:25:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it's okay if she serves you, it's okay if she doesn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.68,0:25:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is different than the one who is willing
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.68,0:25:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,because she's now bringing her own aliveness,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.68,0:25:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,her own intention to say yes, to commit and to agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.68,0:25:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And so real power then begins with this level here
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.68,0:25:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,because you've let go the resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.68,0:25:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So the beauty of neutral is that you've let go resisting things
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.68,0:25:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and you have a lot more power.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.68,0:25:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But now you have to introduce a new energy to move up to 310, which is willingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.32,0:25:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Which moves us to the next field above that called acceptance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.32,0:25:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Acceptance at 380 is a very powerful energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.32,0:25:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the energy field of being capable, adequate and confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.32,0:26:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And at that level there's the beginning of a transformation in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.32,0:26:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.32,0:26:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The transformation has to do with the person's re-owning
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.32,0:26:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that they are the source of their own happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.32,0:26:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That the power is within myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.32,0:26:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And so a person on this level then,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.32,0:26:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the person that a big corporation that has a very big contract,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.32,0:26:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, to get all of Europe or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.32,0:26:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,sends out a person on this level.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.32,0:26:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this person is realistic
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.32,0:26:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in that they can admit their upside and they can admit their downside.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.32,0:26:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,See, they're not into pride, which means denial,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.32,0:26:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,so they can allow for their weaknesses and their shortcomings.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.32,0:26:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So an executive on that level can say,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.32,0:26:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, I don't do very well with that guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.32,0:26:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, in Argentina,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.32,0:26:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, it'd be better if you sent Jake,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.32,0:26:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'd get along better.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.32,0:26:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He can indicate where he's limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.32,0:26:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And a person on a level of acceptance accepts how the world works,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.32,0:26:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,has stopped getting into a right and wrong about it
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.32,0:27:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore can deal with it effectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.32,0:27:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The transformation is because of the re-owning of one's own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.32,0:27:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And a person on this level knows that no matter where you put him,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.32,0:27:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,somehow he will create a circumstance that will create happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.67,0:27:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So that person, if you drop them on a desert island
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.67,0:27:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and you come back a year later,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.67,0:27:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll find that he's, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.67,0:27:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,has a coconut farm going and has built a tree house
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.67,0:27:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and has started a new family with a native girl
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.67,0:27:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and is teaching children French,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.67,0:27:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the person makes out wherever they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.25,0:27:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And the same would be, let's say, putting the person in jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.25,0:27:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So jail is a place, or prison is a place,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.25,0:27:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,where at the bottom of the rung you can commit suicide,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.25,0:27:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you can go into depression and despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.25,0:27:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,or you could become enlightened
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.25,0:27:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,or write a great novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.25,0:27:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, some of the greatest works of literature ever written
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.25,0:27:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,have been written in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.25,0:27:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So a person on this level then would say,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.25,0:27:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,wow, I'm in prison,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.44,0:27:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,at least I got a chance to do what I've always wanted to do all my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.44,0:28:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and sits down and proceeds to write the great novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.44,0:28:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, on the destructive side, something like Mein Kampf, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.44,0:28:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitler wrote Mein Kampf in prison
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.44,0:28:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and practically changed the face of Europe,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.44,0:28:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,changed the face of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.44,0:28:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So the utilization then of opportunity,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.54,0:28:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,coming from this level,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.54,0:28:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,can be turned into turning lemons into lemonade.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.54,0:28:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That comes from a position, a way of being,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.54,0:28:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,a reowning of one's own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.54,0:28:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That leads to a certain easygoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.54,0:28:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So these people are easygoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.54,0:28:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't ruffle easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.24,0:28:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That reowning one's own power, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.24,0:28:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and recycling of the energy back from the universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.24,0:28:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the constant reowning of that
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.24,0:28:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,then moves the person up to an energy field of 500,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.24,0:28:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and we call that love.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.24,0:28:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This type of love is an energy field which is stable,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.75,0:28:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's called unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.75,0:28:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And the emotions that accompany this are
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.75,0:28:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the desire to support,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.75,0:28:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to nurture, to honor all of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.75,0:29:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and forgiveness is part and parcel of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.75,0:29:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,because the motivation there,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.75,0:29:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the purpose there is to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.75,0:29:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So the purpose down here, you see, is to win,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.75,0:29:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,or to make wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.75,0:29:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It becomes a moralistic position.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.75,0:29:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This person up here is not interested in right and wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.75,0:29:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This person is interested in understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.75,0:29:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we talked about the 12-step groups, such as AA,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.75,0:29:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,we characterized them as unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.26,0:29:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is different than what the world calls love.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.00,0:29:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What the world calls love is something down in here
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.00,0:29:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,which is an attachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.00,0:29:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As Solar Plexus says,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.00,0:29:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,sentimentalism, emotionalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.00,0:29:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't live without you, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.00,0:29:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill myself if you leave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.00,0:29:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you if you leave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.00,0:29:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.00,0:29:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll die of loneliness if you walk out of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.00,0:29:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's out of this energy field here that you hear remarks like,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.00,0:29:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to be in love with George, but I'm not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.00,0:29:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What that means is I never was in love with George,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.00,0:30:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but I had a sentimentalism, an emotionalism, an attachment,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.00,0:30:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,a mutual control and dependency,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.00,0:30:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and a lusting after,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.06,0:30:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and an ownership.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.06,0:30:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This kind of love is something that comes from within oneself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.06,0:30:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes from an inner declaration,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.06,0:30:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it comes from an intention,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.06,0:30:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it comes from a realization of truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.06,0:30:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and it comes out as lovingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.06,0:30:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So the person from this energy field then
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.06,0:30:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is loving towards all of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.06,0:30:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,whether the life is a little toad
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.06,0:30:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,or whether the life is standing in sort of a tough love situation
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.06,0:30:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,for the good of someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.06,0:30:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It nurtures and it supports life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.06,0:30:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the beginning of a revelation.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.06,0:30:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And the brain enzyme changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.06,0:30:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got a column here for brain enzymes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.06,0:30:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The brain enzyme changes at the beginning of the release of endorphins.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.06,0:30:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And the release of endorphins then opens millions of banks of neurons,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.06,0:30:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,which up to this time have been sitting around
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.06,0:30:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting for this energy field to activate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.10,0:31:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the whole field of endorphins is the whole field of current research.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.83,0:31:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,At about 540 is the energy field of healing,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.83,0:31:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,healers, people that are touch healers
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.83,0:31:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,or thought healers,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.83,0:31:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the various healing energy fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.83,0:31:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So 540 is the energy field of healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.83,0:31:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And curiously enough, that's the energy field of the 12-step groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.83,0:31:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They come out at about 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.83,0:31:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything that you put in a plus positive energy field of 540 begins to heal,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.96,0:31:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,whether it's a sick animal,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.96,0:31:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,an emotionally sick human being,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.96,0:31:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,an addicted person, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.96,0:31:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A plus energy field of 540 then is healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.96,0:31:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.96,0:31:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a rise in the intensity of the energy field of aliveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.96,0:31:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.96,0:31:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We look to be around those kind of people because they make us feel more alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.18,0:31:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They make us feel more alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.18,0:31:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They give out energy to the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.18,0:32:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,These people down here are pulling energy from the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.18,0:32:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Pulling energy field because they're coming from lack.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.18,0:32:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming from a graspingness, a neediness.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.18,0:32:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And so they tire us and...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.86,0:32:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When this person sits out in the waiting room, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.86,0:32:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and the boss or secretary goes out,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.86,0:32:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,she comes in, she tells the boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.86,0:32:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a guy waiting for you out in front.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.86,0:32:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And with a little flick of the eyebrow, she indicates,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.86,0:32:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.86,0:32:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She's already just gotten the energy field that he came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.86,0:32:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When this person sits out in the waiting room,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.86,0:32:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,he's not going to wait long because they...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.86,0:32:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The secretary instantly gets who that person is and says,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.86,0:32:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,boss, you're running a little bit late.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.86,0:32:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a guy waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.86,0:32:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, she indicates by a flick of an eyebrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.86,0:32:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,this is somebody you don't want to keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.86,0:32:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is somebody you don't want to keep waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.86,0:32:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.86,0:32:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because she's picked up this energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.86,0:32:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a very powerful energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.27,0:32:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,At the bottom, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.27,0:32:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,At the bottom, these are situations of lose-lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.27,0:32:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody loses.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.27,0:33:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You lose and the people that become associated with you
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.27,0:33:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,in your life lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.27,0:33:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And this point of view is one of losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.27,0:33:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So that the person says,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.27,0:33:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,everywhere I look, there's a closed door.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.27,0:33:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do go this way, I'll lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.27,0:33:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If I go this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.27,0:33:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is seen as a losing proposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.37,0:33:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The people in the middle look at life as win-lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.37,0:33:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of their pridefulness,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.37,0:33:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,out of that polarization of angriness,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.37,0:33:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,because they see the world as competition and conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.37,0:33:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,These people live in a world of win-lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.37,0:33:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If I win, therefore you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.37,0:33:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, they have endless unconscious fears of retaliation
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.37,0:33:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,because they look at success as vanquishing
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.37,0:33:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and then expect retaliation.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.37,0:33:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So even if you beat somebody in this game,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.37,0:33:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't really win because, after all,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.37,0:33:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,he's got friends that may come looking for you someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.37,0:33:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can never relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.37,0:33:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,These people up here conceptualize and hold life
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.37,0:33:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,as a win-win situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.37,0:33:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So that when I win, you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.37,0:33:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody in the family wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.37,0:34:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The company wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.37,0:34:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So the more money the company makes,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.37,0:34:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the better for the employees.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.37,0:34:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, everybody tends to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.53,0:34:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So these are win-win situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.53,0:34:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So as we...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.53,0:34:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,just as we avoid these people down here
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.53,0:34:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and tolerate these people in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.53,0:34:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,these people are sought.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.53,0:34:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So these people don't have to look for jobs
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.53,0:34:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,or look for invitations
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.53,0:34:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,or look for relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.53,0:34:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,People seek them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.53,0:34:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,People call them up and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.53,0:34:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you like to work for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.53,0:34:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you like to be vice president of marketing for our company?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.53,0:34:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So people seek you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.53,0:34:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you like to come to our party?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.53,0:34:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you like to go to bed with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.53,0:34:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Et cetera, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.53,0:34:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,These people are sought.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.53,0:34:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And so it comes out of the energy
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.53,0:34:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,field.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.53,0:34:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And as we move up towards 540,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.53,0:34:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,we see there's an inner joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.53,0:34:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Not an emotionalism coming out of the solar plexus
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.53,0:34:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,like you just won the ball game
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.53,0:34:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,jumping up and down,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.53,0:34:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but a quiet inner knowingness
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.53,0:34:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is beginning to take place now
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.53,0:34:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,because at this energy field of revelation,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.53,0:34:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,one connects within oneself
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.53,0:34:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,with something rock-like,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.53,0:35:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,something that is always there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.53,0:35:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And so this is the beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.53,0:35:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of the transfiguration of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.53,0:35:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And we see the beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.53,0:35:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of an inner serenity
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.53,0:35:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and the opening of compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.53,0:35:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And at 560,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.53,0:35:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that reaches actually an ecstasy,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.53,0:35:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,an inner exquisite knowingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.53,0:35:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,a transfiguration of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.53,0:35:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,which is going to be leading up to
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.53,0:35:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,in states really of illumination
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.53,0:35:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,as we get close to 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.82,0:35:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This energy field of compassion
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.82,0:35:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is one which one can elect.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.82,0:35:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There are several places one can elect.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.82,0:35:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,One certainly has a choice here
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.82,0:35:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to tell the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.82,0:35:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and bring oneself up to this energy field here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.82,0:35:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,One can make a commitment
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.82,0:35:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to lovingness as a way of being.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.82,0:35:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So this requires no belief in God
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.82,0:35:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,or any theological, spiritual system.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.82,0:35:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That commitment to lovingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.82,0:35:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to that which nurtures and supports life
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.82,0:36:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in all of its expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.82,0:36:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It sees that which is divine in all things
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.82,0:36:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,as it moves up to an even higher level
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.82,0:36:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,where it begins to see the perfection of all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.62,0:36:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Compassion then is a way of knowing,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.62,0:36:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,a way of looking into the hearts of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.62,0:36:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, because of the release of endorphins
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.62,0:36:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,here at this level of revelation,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.62,0:36:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the beginning of transfiguration,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.62,0:36:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,there comes that knowing,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.62,0:36:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the separation between one self as an individual
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.62,0:36:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and another self as an individual
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.62,0:36:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to break down.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.62,0:36:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's almost like the beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.62,0:36:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,of a oneness of the heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.62,0:36:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,a knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.62,0:36:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a thinkingness, but a knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.62,0:36:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Different than thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.65,0:36:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something we're missing on the board here
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.65,0:36:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is the energy fields in here
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.65,0:36:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,because we don't have enough room
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.65,0:36:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to put it on the blackboard,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.65,0:36:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of the four hundreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.65,0:36:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the four hundreds are the level of mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.65,0:36:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of intellect, of thinkingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.65,0:37:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of the process going on in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.65,0:37:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of conceptualization.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.65,0:37:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Conceptualization.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.65,0:37:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.13,0:37:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is mind in the four hundreds,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.13,0:37:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,thinkingness, intellect, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.13,0:37:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And above that is heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.13,0:37:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see the statement that says
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.13,0:37:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that the thing that differentiates man from the animal,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.13,0:37:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the thing that makes the man the highest of all things
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.13,0:37:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is his intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.13,0:37:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't come out here correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.13,0:37:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's man's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.13,0:37:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the heart you see is higher than the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.13,0:37:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The heart, which doesn't think, just knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.13,0:37:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So at this energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.13,0:37:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is knowingness without the necessity for thinkingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.13,0:37:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,See, and the god of mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.13,0:37:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the god of the intellect,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.13,0:37:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.13,0:37:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And the worship of intelligence then,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.13,0:37:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,being in the four hundreds,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.13,0:37:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is certainly higher than these
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.13,0:37:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of demonic levels down below.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.13,0:37:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is still a far cry from
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.13,0:38:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,those states of the full opening of the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.13,0:38:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So that love, the energy field of heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.13,0:38:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,then begins about here
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.13,0:38:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and goes up to infinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.13,0:38:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So love, we begin to detect that at five hundred,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.16,0:38:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the energy field of happiness, by the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.16,0:38:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,begins at five hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.16,0:38:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But then that expands up into infinity
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.16,0:38:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,through the six hundred, seven hundred, eight hundred,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.16,0:38:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,up to a thousand and beyond.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.16,0:38:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So these are the beginning of the energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.16,0:38:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but by no means the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.16,0:38:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the beginning and it goes on to infinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.16,0:38:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This level of revelation then opens our way
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.74,0:38:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to transfiguration and this compassion
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.74,0:38:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,which leads to ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.74,0:38:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And leads up to the states close to six hundred,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.74,0:38:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,which are states of bliss,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.74,0:38:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the beginning of states of illumination
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.74,0:38:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and enlightenment and experientially
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.74,0:38:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,they are often accompanied by feelings of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.74,0:38:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, the room lit up.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.74,0:38:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,When Bill Wilson, for instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.74,0:38:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,had his spiritual experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.74,0:38:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,he said the room lit up by the infinite presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.74,0:39:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was the beginning of the approach
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.74,0:39:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,of that energy field of six hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.74,0:39:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field is up here called bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.74,0:39:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that was very important in our talk on addiction
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.74,0:39:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,because we said that the energy field of bliss
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.74,0:39:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,transforms the person's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.74,0:39:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who falls into samadhi by accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.74,0:39:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,goes into a transcendental state.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.74,0:39:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So six hundred and up are transcendental states.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.74,0:39:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually that person's life is changed thereafter.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.74,0:39:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,People who have near-death experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.74,0:39:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and experience those energy fields over six hundred
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.74,0:39:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,experience the presence of their own higher self,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.74,0:39:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the conscious awareness of one solar angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.74,0:39:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are levels beyond which
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.74,0:39:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,then go on up to infinity
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.74,0:39:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and the various world famous spiritual teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.74,0:39:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's a whole subject in itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.74,0:39:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the subject of what goes on in the six hundreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.74,0:39:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We can say roughly that
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.74,0:39:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the beginning of the energy field of the Christ and the Buddha
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.74,0:39:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is around seven hundred and fifty to eight hundred
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.74,0:39:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and then goes from there on up to infinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.74,0:40:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the levels which have such enormous power
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.74,0:40:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that we call them avatars.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.74,0:40:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,An avatar in three years of his ministry
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.74,0:40:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the Christ totally transformed and changed the consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.74,0:40:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,of all mankind for thousands of years to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.74,0:40:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Transformed our life on the horizontal plane
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.15,0:40:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as the vertical.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.15,0:40:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And so those are fields of enormous power.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.22,0:40:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least it gives us an idea now
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.22,0:40:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,where all this fits together.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.22,0:40:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And we said that this energy field here
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.38,0:40:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,can be experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.38,0:40:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,by removing one's experience of these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.38,0:40:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the sun is always shining
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.38,0:40:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and these energy fields here are like the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.38,0:40:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And as we remove the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.38,0:40:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,we experience the sun which is always shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.47,0:40:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the talk on addictions
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.47,0:40:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,we made a very precise point
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.47,0:40:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's not the removal of the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.47,0:40:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that causes the sun to shine
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.47,0:40:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,which is what the addicted person begins to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.47,0:40:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now people who get addicted to anything
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.47,0:41:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking that because of the left brain
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.47,0:41:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,type of thinking linear causes
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.47,0:41:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,causality that A causes B causes C.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.60,0:41:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The removal of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.60,0:41:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So the whole purpose of spiritual work then
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.60,0:41:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is the removal of these clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.60,0:41:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so that one experiences the shining forth
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.60,0:41:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,of the self with a capital S
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.60,0:41:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,which is at the top of the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.59,0:41:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,These energy fields then are so powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.59,0:41:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,they dominate our perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.59,0:41:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They're really portholes out of which we see the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.59,0:41:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And we often hear it said that this is really
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.59,0:41:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,just a world of mirrors.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.59,0:41:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That all we're experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.59,0:41:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is our own energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.59,0:41:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,controlling our perception and our experiencing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.59,0:41:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's look at that then.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.59,0:41:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look at perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.59,0:41:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look at the view of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.59,0:41:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and the view of life
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.59,0:41:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,as it comes out of these various energy fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.59,0:41:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,As we said in the beginning, guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.33,0:41:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that self-hatred, that destructive energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.42,0:41:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,sees a world of sin and suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.42,0:42:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore that person walking down the street
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.42,0:42:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,looks around and all that person sees is suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.42,0:42:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And when they open the newspaper
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.42,0:42:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,what they see is the endless suffering of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.42,0:42:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who is in this energy field here
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.06,0:42:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,of hopelessness and despair
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.06,0:42:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,literally sees a hopeless world.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.06,0:42:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And when he opens the newspaper
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.06,0:42:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,he notices the hopeless condition of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.06,0:42:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the endless wars, the endless poverty,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.06,0:42:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the endless crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.22,0:42:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And so actually experiences perceptually,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.22,0:42:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,visually, auditorily, through all the senses
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.22,0:42:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,experiences a world
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.22,0:42:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.51,0:42:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So what kind of a God could be the God
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.51,0:42:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of a hopeless world as we said
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.51,0:42:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,this is God is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.51,0:42:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The person in grief, regret and loss and despondency
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.74,0:42:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that dispirited state
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.74,0:42:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,coming out of the loss of the will to live
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.74,0:42:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,walks down the street and sees this as a sad world.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.77,0:43:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is what is actually experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.77,0:43:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and you know yourself if you're in a sad state
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.77,0:43:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,when you walk down the street
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.77,0:43:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the children and you think
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.77,0:43:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,how sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.77,0:43:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You know you look at the old people
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.77,0:43:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and you think how sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.77,0:43:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You look at the buildings
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.77,0:43:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you look at mankind's condition
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.77,0:43:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and you think how sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.77,0:43:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And as I said you open the newspaper
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.77,0:43:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see how sad is life.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.77,0:43:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your own energy field coloring everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.77,0:43:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So these are like colored glasses
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.77,0:43:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and we put them on
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.77,0:43:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and we then experience everything
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.77,0:43:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,as being colored by this energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.77,0:43:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The person in fear as we well know
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.57,0:43:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,sees this as a threatening world
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.57,0:43:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,a frightening world.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.57,0:43:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Constant jeopardy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.57,0:43:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So he sees it as a world of danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.57,0:43:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So the person walking down the street
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.57,0:43:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,in that energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.57,0:43:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,sees danger everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.57,0:43:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sees that you could break your ankle here
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.57,0:43:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,break your ankle there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.57,0:43:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They cover everything with insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.57,0:43:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They see the threat
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.57,0:43:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,muggers everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.57,0:43:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and rapers under the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.57,0:43:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course when they open the newspaper
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.57,0:44:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,they see the frightening conditions of all of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.57,0:44:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The jeopardy, the danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.57,0:44:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And they live in their house
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.57,0:44:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,they lock their car
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.57,0:44:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and their own garage
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.57,0:44:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and then they lock the garage
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.57,0:44:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,which is in their house which is locked
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.57,0:44:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,which is in their yard which is locked
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.57,0:44:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,which is in a neighborhood
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.57,0:44:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,which has never had a robbery yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.57,0:44:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet the fear goes on you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.57,0:44:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So having more police doesn't really help
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.57,0:44:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,because where are the police going to be
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.57,0:44:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,when your house is robbed?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.57,0:44:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You know where they're going to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.57,0:44:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to be at the other end of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.57,0:44:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So it doesn't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.82,0:44:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So trying to change the world then
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.82,0:44:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't really assuage it
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.82,0:44:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's coming from one's own energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.82,0:44:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The field above that
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.78,0:44:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,desiringness then sees this
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.78,0:44:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,as a frustrating world of endless wantingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.78,0:44:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the person coming from this energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.78,0:44:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of wantingness
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.78,0:44:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,this solar plexus fixation
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.78,0:44:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,as they walk down the street
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.78,0:44:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,they see all the things they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.78,0:44:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They see the cars they want
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.78,0:44:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the beauty that they want
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.78,0:44:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the status, the positions
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.78,0:44:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the buildings they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.78,0:45:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So because the world is therefore frustrating
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.78,0:45:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,because of their endless wantingness
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.78,0:45:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,which can never be satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.78,0:45:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the multi-millionaire
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.78,0:45:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,whose fingernails grow long
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.78,0:45:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and their hair grows long
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.78,0:45:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and they get paranoid and weird
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.78,0:45:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,as they get older.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.78,0:45:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,More and more millions of dollars
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.78,0:45:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't satisfy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.78,0:45:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that they have 50 million doesn't help
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.78,0:45:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,because the desiring, the wanting
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.78,0:45:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,for more power.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.78,0:45:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So these are fields then
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.78,0:45:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that cannot be satisfied
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.78,0:45:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and this frustration leads to anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.78,0:45:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So the angry world then sees
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.78,0:45:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the angry person then sees
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.78,0:45:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,a competitive world
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.78,0:45:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,a world of conflict, of war
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.78,0:45:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of me against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.78,0:45:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The person into this competitive view of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.78,0:45:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,looks out in the woods
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.78,0:45:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and thinks that the tall trees are competing
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.78,0:45:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,with the small trees for the sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.78,0:45:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see this is a conception
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.82,0:45:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,then projected on to a field
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.82,0:45:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,where there is no such thing as competition
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.82,0:45:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,even going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.82,0:45:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And so that person lives in a world
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.82,0:46:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of endless possibility of war
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.82,0:46:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and conflict
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.82,0:46:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and they see everything as competition
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.82,0:46:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,not as cooperation
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.82,0:46:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,which a person up here would see.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.82,0:46:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who is into pride
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.82,0:46:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,sees this as a world of status
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.82,0:46:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and so that person walking down the same street
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.82,0:46:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,sees the Gucci shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.82,0:46:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,sees the name tags
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.82,0:46:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and sees the labels
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.82,0:46:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,sees the status
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.82,0:46:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't see grief or any of this at all
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.82,0:46:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,only sees the kind of car they would want
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.82,0:46:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the kind of building they would like to live
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.82,0:46:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,they classify everything in terms of status
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.82,0:46:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and so positionality
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.82,0:46:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,they are preoccupied with positionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.82,0:46:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens when you get to the level of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.82,0:46:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the level of courage
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.82,0:46:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the world suddenly appears
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.82,0:46:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,as a place of opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.82,0:46:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is an exciting challenging place
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.82,0:46:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,an opportunity for growth and expansion
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.82,0:46:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that person opens the newspaper
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.82,0:46:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and sees the endless opportunities
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.82,0:46:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,for man to grow
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.82,0:46:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to meet these challenges
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.82,0:46:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to go beyond them
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.82,0:46:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to learn in the process
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.82,0:47:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and so that person is excited about life.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.23,0:47:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As we move up to neutral then
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.23,0:47:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,we move into a world of okayness
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.23,0:47:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,because this person is detached
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.23,0:47:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,unattached
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.23,0:47:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,rather non-attached
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.23,0:47:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,everything sort of becomes okay
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.23,0:47:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and you start moving into an easy going view of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.23,0:47:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,in which the person begins to say
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.23,0:47:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,well that's human nature
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.23,0:47:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the way it is
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.23,0:47:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it's serving some kind of an ultimate purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.23,0:47:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who moves into willingness
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.30,0:47:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,now for the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.30,0:47:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to experience this as a friendly world
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.30,0:47:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and that person walking down the street
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.30,0:47:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,sees the endless friendlinesses that go on
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.30,0:47:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,how friendly this universe is
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.30,0:47:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what you have
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.30,0:47:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,like you pull your nose in a hanky
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.30,0:47:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a waste basket right there
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.30,0:47:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the world is harmonious
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.30,0:47:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and friendly and supportive.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.36,0:47:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The person on the level of acceptance then
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.36,0:47:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,really experiences that harmony of life
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.36,0:47:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to experience what Jung calls synchronicity
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.36,0:47:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,how everything just sort of flows together
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.36,0:47:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and begins to experience a world of cooperation
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.36,0:48:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,because he's holding cooperation
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.36,0:48:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,as his own energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.36,0:48:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,he experiences life as cooperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.36,0:48:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This person as he moves into lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.39,0:48:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to experience the lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.39,0:48:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and the endless loving support
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.39,0:48:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the universality of that loving energy in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.39,0:48:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The person moving up towards states of illumination
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.39,0:48:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to experience the incredible beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.39,0:48:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and perfection of life
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.39,0:48:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the absolute perfection of creation
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.39,0:48:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and as he moves up towards the highest energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.39,0:48:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,he experiences actually the divine essence
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.39,0:48:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and nature of all of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.39,0:48:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The incredible beauty of all things
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.39,0:48:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,not aesthetic beauty which is pleasing to the senses
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.39,0:48:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but the intrinsic beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.39,0:48:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,which when you walk down an alley
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.39,0:48:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,which to the eye of the unenlightened would look ugly
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.39,0:48:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,experiences the incredible perfection and beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.39,0:48:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,of the aliveness of life
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.39,0:48:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to see all of life as a rose unfolding
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.39,0:48:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,so he doesn't see imperfection
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.39,0:48:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,sees process
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.39,0:49:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that person there instead of being wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.39,0:49:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,is in the unfoldment
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.39,0:49:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,sees all of the universe as the unfoldment of that perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.39,0:49:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So what kind of a God can one envision
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.81,0:49:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,from these various energy fields then?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.81,0:49:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,As we said this person here
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.81,0:49:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,envisions a God who is the ultimate destroyer
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.81,0:49:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and actually the ultimate enemy and hater of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.81,0:49:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the ultimate of hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.81,0:49:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,To throw your eternal soul into hell forever
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.38,0:49:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,would be the ultimate act of hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.38,0:49:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The person in apathy and hopelessness
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.80,0:49:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,experiences God as dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.80,0:49:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who is in this energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.80,0:49:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes says I believe in God
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.80,0:49:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but I feel he wouldn't have anything to do with me
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.80,0:49:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,because I am just a worm, worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.80,0:49:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so worthless that God would have nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.80,0:49:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who lives in fear
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.80,0:49:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,sees a punitive, frightening, terrifying God.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.80,0:49:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who lives in frustration
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.93,0:49:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,feels separated from God.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.93,0:49:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the God who constantly whispers.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.93,0:50:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the God who constantly withholds from you
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.93,0:50:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that which would allow you to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.93,0:50:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore he is actually acting in a very hostile manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.93,0:50:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The person in anger expects, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.93,0:50:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,a retaliatory, punishing God.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.93,0:50:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And because these things go together
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.93,0:50:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,we then get the God who is really demonic.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.93,0:50:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The God who really hates you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.93,0:50:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Who threatens to throw you into hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.93,0:50:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The ultimate destroyer, the punisher.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.93,0:50:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The God who is vengeful.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.93,0:50:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The God who is jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.93,0:50:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So we get a depiction of a God who is fitfully jealous
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.93,0:50:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and given to emotional extremes of destructiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.93,0:50:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all coming out, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.93,0:50:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,of a field of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.93,0:50:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,having no basis in reality whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.93,0:50:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,When we get up to here, the level of pride
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.06,0:50:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,we can have two directions to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.06,0:50:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the arrogance.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.06,0:50:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the inflated ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.06,0:50:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We can have, on the one hand, atheism
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.06,0:50:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,or on the other side, the zealot.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.06,0:50:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The bigot. The one who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.06,0:51:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So these are people who have the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.06,0:51:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And the answer is coming out of intellectual arrogance.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.38,0:51:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,As we move up to courage, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.38,0:51:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the level of truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.38,0:51:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,what kind of God do we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.38,0:51:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We have God of a question mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.38,0:51:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,For the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.38,0:51:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,because we're now hitting the level of truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.38,0:51:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,we have an open mind and the person says,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.38,0:51:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, I really don't know about God.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.38,0:51:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only hearsay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.38,0:51:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All that I've read, all that I've heard,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.44,0:51:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,all that religion teaches
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.44,0:51:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is really other people's experience
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.44,0:51:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,in times and places.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.44,0:51:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And on the witness stand, frankly,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.44,0:51:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have to say, I don't know anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.44,0:51:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the question mark, the spiritual seeking,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.44,0:51:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,really begins at this level.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.44,0:51:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The person says, I of my own self
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.44,0:51:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,would like to know what is the truth of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.44,0:51:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you move into the God of one's own inner experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.11,0:51:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The God of one's own understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.27,0:51:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,As you move up to this level of neutral, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.27,0:51:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you begin to experience a world of okayness
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.27,0:51:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and you experience, as we said before,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.27,0:52:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,God as freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.27,0:52:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You begin to experience that there is no punitive,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.27,0:52:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,hateful, negative God at all
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.27,0:52:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,because you've moved out of those energy fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.27,0:52:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a God of absolute, infinite freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.27,0:52:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to expand, to explore, to become,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.27,0:52:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to fulfill one's potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.34,0:52:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,As we move up to the willingness, friendly level,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.34,0:52:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,we begin to experience God as something
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.34,0:52:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that is perhaps promising and hopeful.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.34,0:52:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that is now positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.34,0:52:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Down here it was negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.34,0:52:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it opens to openness and freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.34,0:52:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But now it's beginning to look positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.34,0:52:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And the person on this level here,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.34,0:52:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,experiencing life as harmony,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.34,0:52:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,realizes God is the ultimate merciful.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.34,0:52:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The ultimate, that which is all forgiving
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.37,0:52:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and all merciful.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.37,0:52:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And the person in lovingness, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.37,0:52:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to experience the God of unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.37,0:52:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The ever presence of the love of God
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.37,0:52:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,as the source of one's happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.37,0:52:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and the source of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.37,0:52:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,As we move into joy and the awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.37,0:53:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,of beauty and perfection
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.37,0:53:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and the divine essence of all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.37,0:53:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The oneness of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.37,0:53:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The oneness, the unity.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.37,0:53:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally we move to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.37,0:53:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,God as beingness, isness, the reality, the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.37,0:53:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.37,0:53:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is nameless.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.37,0:53:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And one realizes that one is at one with that
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.37,0:53:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,as one goes into 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.37,0:53:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We now have a context
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.37,0:53:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,which will give a certain
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.37,0:53:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,background, a way to hold now
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.37,0:53:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and to see our spiritual work
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.37,0:53:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,from a different perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.37,0:53:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,To see healing from a different perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.37,0:53:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How to approach that
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.37,0:53:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,great enigma called the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.94,0:53:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We see now that
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.94,0:53:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,this energy field of 540 and up,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.94,0:53:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the fields of compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.94,0:53:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We're interested in compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.94,0:53:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And people in spiritual work are generally
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.94,0:53:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,perfecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.94,0:53:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming from the 400s
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.94,0:53:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,where they have learningness,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.94,0:53:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,knowledge with a small k about spiritual matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.94,0:54:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting them into effect
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.94,0:54:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and trying to perfect the 500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.94,0:54:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course the miracles,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.94,0:54:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the 12-step groups,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.94,0:54:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,a great many are concerned with
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.94,0:54:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the perfecting of the capacity to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.01,0:54:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And we move up to a certain way then
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.01,0:54:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,of viewing what the world calls the ego then.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.04,0:54:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If we, you see money in and of itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.04,0:54:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,let's take an example of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.04,0:54:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Money, wealth, power, sexuality,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.04,0:54:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,worldly success is all around 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.04,0:54:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember in that movie Lost Horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.17,0:54:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,where the hero falls into Shangri-La
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.17,0:54:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,which calibrates at about 625.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.17,0:54:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He comes back into the world of doingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.17,0:54:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the world of doingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.17,0:54:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And he no longer finds satisfaction
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.42,0:54:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because he has experienced something higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.42,0:54:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You see at the bottom of the box here,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.42,0:54:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the world of havingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.42,0:54:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what you have that counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.42,0:54:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And people, status,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.42,0:54:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,etc. comes from what you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.42,0:55:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In the middle of the box,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.42,0:55:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the world of doingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.42,0:55:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,At the bottom they want to know what you have
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.42,0:55:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and they rate you on what you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.42,0:55:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The world of doingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.42,0:55:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,they want to know what you do in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.42,0:55:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do there?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.42,0:55:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, what position,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.42,0:55:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,what is your function?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.42,0:55:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Havingness is no longer impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.42,0:55:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Down here at Cadillac it's very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.42,0:55:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it's no longer so impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.42,0:55:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because everybody knows if you do plenty,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.42,0:55:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,like work seven days a week and two jobs,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.42,0:55:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can have all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.42,0:55:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So havingness then no longer has status.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.42,0:55:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Doingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.42,0:55:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But as you move towards the top of the box,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.42,0:55:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not what you have,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.42,0:55:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not what you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.42,0:55:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it's what you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.42,0:55:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it's what you have become.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.42,0:55:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,People seek you out now
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.42,0:55:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,for what you have become,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.42,0:55:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,what you have,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.42,0:55:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth that you have owned about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.42,0:55:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we seek those people
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.42,0:55:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because of what they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.42,0:55:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even care what they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.42,0:55:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've known people like that for many years
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.42,0:55:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and I never have known what they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.42,0:55:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't know what they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.42,0:56:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But what they are is what is interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.42,0:56:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and why we seek their company.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.42,0:56:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So, utilizing this knowledge then,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.97,0:56:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,we have an understanding of many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.97,0:56:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The way to heal the small self then
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.06,0:56:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is not to come from a polarized right-wrong position,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.06,0:56:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,a make-wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.06,0:56:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,which makes it our enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.06,0:56:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and gives it energy and power,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.06,0:56:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but to come from a loving compassion,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.06,0:56:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to see the intrinsic,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.06,0:56:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to see the intrinsic innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.06,0:56:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Because within this here,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.06,0:56:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,what you see is the innocence of the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.06,0:56:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the innocence of the child's consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.06,0:56:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you see the programming that comes in.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.06,0:56:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of the child's lovingness and trustiness
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.06,0:56:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that it is so programmable.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.06,0:56:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And you begin to see the innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.06,0:56:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,even within that which is most hateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.10,0:56:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of one's compassion then,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.10,0:56:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to see into the hearts of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.10,0:56:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,one sees the intrinsic innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.10,0:56:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,even within the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.10,0:56:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, how does it get healed then?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.10,0:57:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets healed out of compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.10,0:57:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.10,0:57:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We love our humanness.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.10,0:57:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of condemning it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.10,0:57:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,we say,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.10,0:57:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I see the necessity of that at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.10,0:57:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.10,0:57:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of being ashamed of anger,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.10,0:57:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,hatred,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.10,0:57:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,we say to ourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.10,0:57:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,well, that being angry was necessary at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.10,0:57:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Because a person who's never hated
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.10,0:57:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,will never move up to love, will they?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.10,0:57:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they've never cared that much about love,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.10,0:57:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,life.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.10,0:57:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't care enough about life
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.10,0:57:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to have ever gotten angry
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.10,0:57:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and actually hated,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.10,0:57:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,then you would be down here in apathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.10,0:57:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So we look at our humanness then
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.10,0:57:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,from the viewpoint of forgiveness,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.10,0:57:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,from compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.10,0:57:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And we love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.10,0:57:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We hold it within our greatness.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.10,0:57:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And we look at our smallness
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.10,0:57:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,like we look at the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.10,0:57:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And we begin to heal it through understanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.10,0:57:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,through compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.10,0:57:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we do, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.10,0:57:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,we're pulling forth a very powerful energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.10,0:57:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,a healing energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.10,0:57:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When we look at ourself
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.10,0:57:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,from compassion and from lovingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.10,0:58:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,we begin to heal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.10,0:58:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course we know
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.10,0:58:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that which we forgive in others
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.10,0:58:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is forgiven within ourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.10,0:58:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That which we forgive in ourself
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.10,0:58:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,disappears from our perception of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.10,0:58:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So our perception of the world begins to shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.10,0:58:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And as we hit the level of 600,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.10,0:58:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,we begin to experience a world
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.10,0:58:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,which is totally different.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.10,0:58:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I always say,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.10,0:58:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,movie A is replaced by movie B.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.10,0:58:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you're putting on different colored glasses
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.10,0:58:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and now it looks the same
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.10,0:58:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's experienced totally differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.13,0:58:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And so that's the purpose of this map of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.13,0:58:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to create a context
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.13,0:58:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which merely experiencing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.13,0:58:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,merely seeing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.13,0:58:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,opens whole new avenues.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.13,0:58:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Whole new avenues begin to just open up automatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.13,0:58:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And our intention,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.13,0:58:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,our intention now is facilitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.13,0:58:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Our capacity to heal ourself
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.13,0:58:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and to heal others,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.13,0:58:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the fulfillment of our own potential,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.13,0:58:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,as we see ourself move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.13,0:58:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,in our own realization of the truth.
